1 A BILL FOR AN ACT relating to appropriations; to appropriate funds to aid
2 in carrying out the provisions of Legislative Bill 365, One Hundred
3 Ninth Legislature, Second Session, 2026.
4 Be it enacted by the people of the State of Nebraska,
-1-

LB365A LB365A
2026 2026
1 Section 1. There is hereby appropriated (1) $9,634 from the General
2 Fund and $15,476 from federal funds for FY2026-27 and (2) $19,268 from
3 the General Fund and $30,952 from federal funds for FY2027-28 to the
4 Department of Health and Human Services, for Program 348, to aid in
5 carrying out the provisions of Legislative Bill 365, One Hundred Ninth
6 Legislature, Second Session, 2026.
7 There is included in the appropriation to this program for FY2026-27
8 $9,634 General Funds and $15,476 federal funds for state aid, which shall
9 only be used for such purpose. There is included in the appropriation to
10 this program for FY2027-28 $19,268 General Funds and $30,952 federal
11 funds for state aid, which shall only be used for such purpose.
12 No expenditures for permanent and temporary salaries and per diems
13 for state employees shall be made from funds appropriated in this
14 section.
